data.description: You can be on vacation all the time while you dwell a stone's throw away from the Santa Monica beach in this two bedroom, two bath condo. You will also be one block from Main Street with its posh restaurants and shops if you live in the prestigious Sea Colony III.  Lush greenery surrounds this condo and can be seen and breathed in from all the windows.  Throughout the inside of this condo, there are magnificent floors.  As for Sea Colony III, there are many up to date amenities. There are spas, pool, and a state of the art gym.
